### 11. KEY PATTERNS SUMMARY

| Aspect | Pattern |
|--------|---------|
| **Task Definition** | Frozen Object.freeze() with standardized keys: tokenizer, pipeline, model, processor, default, type |
| **Aliases** | Optional shortcuts mapped in TASK_ALIASES Object.freeze() |
| **Output Type** | typedef ObjectName + ObjectName[] (single/array variants) |
| **Options Type** | typedef PipelineNamePipelineOptions with JSDoc @property for each option |
| **Callback** | @callback signature with @param for each argument and @returns |
| **Constructor Args** | Pre-built typedefs (TextPipelineConstructorArgs, AudioPipelineConstructorArgs, etc.) |
| **Combined Type** | `@typedef {ConstructorArgs & Callback & Disposable} PipelineType` |
| **Class Doc** | Prose description + 2-3 **Example** blocks with code fences |
| **Implementation** | `async _call(inputs, {options}={})` method with type annotation |
| **Disposal** | All pipelines have `async dispose()` method |
| **Batch Support** | Pipelines check `Array.isArray()` and handle both single/batch returns |
| **Test Structure** | beforeAll setup, describe batch_size scenarios, afterAll cleanup |

